TimeSaver.rexx V1.1b (29-Mar-1998)

An ARexx script to auto-adjust inaccurate battery backed-up clocks.
Written by Ralf Schönfeldt (Freeware)

    I.@{" Introduction " link "Introduction"}
   II.@{" Disclaimer   " link "Disclaimer"}
